  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>睿兽分析</span> <span>2026-03-22 09:05</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b93d37a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F03KNO9Fib2w4p7AwHjdzzfXbdOPLHn3G1OAiajbc9oziawWRRUGS8hSr00Jfia0cZxrw7y0bmgvNWvHDsnyU2A4ZnA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>每日AI资讯速递。</p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkmairwf2156\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmym6u3f16p6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTAzMjc4MA==&amp;mid=2650613578&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=67196d4e6b88c18cf8596bd89cab5e59&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w4p7AwHjdzzfXbdOPLHn3G1ozbTDyYO66bg6pjkpMgSMW8efuibbGEZX8BzqLnU7Zs9YGmOR8PRfvg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;width:100%;\" class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"232\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w4p7AwHjdzzfXbdOPLHn3G1ozbTDyYO66bg6pjkpMgSMW8efuibbGEZX8BzqLnU7Zs9YGmOR8PRfvg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"201\" data-imgfileid=\"503354894\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d20efe03&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w4p7AwHjdzzfXbdOPLHn3G1ozbTDyYO66bg6pjkpMgSMW8efuibbGEZX8BzqLnU7Zs9YGmOR8PRfvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></a>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmym6u2n193a\">1.【阿里妈妈发布超级经营智能体引擎“AI万相”】3月21日消息，阿里妈妈发布其超级经营智能体引擎“AI万相”，商家只需要下达经营指令，“AI万相”负责从拆解任务到交付成交的所有复杂环节。（界面新闻）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmym6u2n15tr\">2.【</span><span data-v-19a677c5=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\">Cursor承认新模型基于Kimi训练并致歉】</span></span><span data-v-19a677c5=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\">3月21日消息，本周五，全球知名编程工具Cursor宣布上线Composer 2，称在基准测试中击败Claude 4.6 Opus，成为目前最强编程模型。但很快有开发者发现Composer 2是在Kimi K2.5上训练的，马斯克也亲自下场指认。今天凌晨，Cursor联合创始人Aman Sanger发文并致歉，称“没有在博客中从一开始就提及Kimi基础模型是我们的疏漏，会在下一个模型中修正这一点。”Kimi官方账号随后表示：“恭喜Cursor推出Composer 2，很骄傲看到Kimi K2.5成为基础模型，这就是我们喜欢的开源生态。”据报道，Cursor正以500亿美元估值进行融资。（东方财富网）</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmym6u2ngeq\">3.</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\">【xAI派工程师上门服务，争夺OpenAI企业客户】马斯克旗下的xAI正在向潜在企业客户派遣工程师，力图从OpenAI和Anthropic等竞争对手手中争夺业务。这种上门服务策略已帮助xAI赢得支付公司Shift4 Payments Inc.，后者计划逐步淘汰OpenAI的ChatGPT，转而采用xAI的Grok。Shift4 CEO表示，公司仍将使用Anthropic的Claude进行代码开发。（财联社）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mkmairwf2156&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagNa